Rating: 3
Even with all the ingredients, this was actually really easy to make. I don't have a food processor, so I just used my blender and it took a bit of creativity, but I think the best way is to first put all the ingredients EXCEPT for the bulgur/bean mix into the blender and pulse those. Then add the bulgur and mix and pulse until it is a satisfying consistency. These didn't fall apart as other reviewers lamented. I didn't touch my burgers once they were in the pan, only turning them halfway through the cooking time. Make sure your pan is super hot and your burgers and chilled thoroughly. Good Middle-Eastern taste, but this was more like falafel than a veggie burger...

